<br>
Our guild is not likely to qualify anytime soon for RTA planable status, for many reasons, mostly because the core members have a different attitude about the game.<br>
<br>
However, I strongly support the RTA system we have on this server, I keep an eye on what is happening so that I can find raids for our guild members who need assistance on planable items and epic peices.<br>
<br>
My guild is not on rotation nor do we have posting status on the calendar, but it hasn't inhibited our play at all. If you are civil to people and helpful, those same guilds you are criticizing will be happy to take you along and help you out to do things you might not otherwise be able to do.<br>
<br>
And I would like to point out that if Broken doesn't like the social conventions on this server, there are many more servers to try out, they all have their own unique social conventions.<br>
<br>
Toric Seerson<br>
