<br>
With the RTA even though it may seem a allmighty crushing fist, the smaller guilds have a chance at least of getting the mobs rather than being run over by the larger guilds while you are forming up.<br>
<br>
Heck even Vox &amp; Nagafen don't last an hour if someone finds out they have spawned.  Here, they could be up for 10-12 hours or more waiting for guild on rotation to come get them.<br>
<br>
If I'm wrong on some points its because I only have one planable toon and have not had to deal with the specifics with RTA.<br>
<br>
So, in parting.  At least smaller guilds have a chance.  If you don't have enough people on your own to make rotation, talk to some of the other smaller guilds that are in the same boat and get an alliance going.  It works until you have enough force and you make friends in the process. <p><HTML><BODY><center>
